              <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Monthly Cost</th>
              <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Users Included</th>
              <th style="padding: 12px; text-align: left; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Break-Even Point</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Essential</td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">$299/month</td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Unlimited</td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">6+ users vs Jobber</td>
            </tr>
            <tr style="background-color: #f8f9fa;">
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Professional</td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">$499/month</td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Unlimited</td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">8+ users vs Housecall Pro</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Enterprise</td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">$799+ (custom)</td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">Unlimited</td>
              <td style="padding: 12px; border: 1px solid #ddd;">15+ users vs ServiceTitan</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>

        <h2 id="total-cost-breakdown">Total Cost Breakdown for HVAC</h2>

        <p>Service Fusion's base pricing doesn't include everything HVAC companies need. Here's what 5-person and 15-person teams actually pay monthly:</p>

        <h3>5-Person HVAC Company Total Costs</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Essential plan: $299/month</li>
          <li>QuickBooks integration: $25/month</li>
          <li>Advanced inventory: $50/month</li>
          <li>Payment processing: 2.9% + $0.30 per transaction</li>
          <li><strong>Total: $374/month minimum</strong></li>
        </ul>

        <p>For comparison, <a href="/hvac/pricing/jobber-pricing">Jobber would cost $245/month</a> for the same 5-person team with equivalent features.</p>

        <h3>15-Person HVAC Company Total Costs</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Professional plan: $499/month</li>
          <li>Advanced reporting: $75/month</li>
          <li>API access: $100/month</li>
          <li>Priority support: $150/month</li>
          <li><strong>Total: $824/month</strong></li>
        </ul>

        <p>This compares favorably to ServiceTitan, which would cost $3,000+ monthly for 15 users. Read our <a href="/hvac/pricing/servicetitan-pricing">ServiceTitan pricing breakdown</a> for detailed comparisons.</p>

