            <a href="https://housecallpro.partnerlinks.io/auy5xcz257sw" rel="sponsored nofollow" style="background-color: #27AE60; color: white; padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem; border-radius: 6px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600;">Try Housecall Pro</a>
